In the midst of his reaction, he inquired as to whether or not other people are truly seeing what he is seeing. He continued by saying that even the large state of Kaduna is not excluded from this either.
Joe Igbokwe has demonstrated on multiple occasions that he is a staunch supporter of Bola Ahmed Tinubu by promoting him on social media, and with the way things are going at the moment, it appears that he is not going to be stopping anytime soon.
